# Dovecot passwd-file — copy to "users" and add your accounts.
# Format: user:password:uid:gid:gecos:home:shell
# Use local part as user (e.g. user1 for user1@localhost).
# Password: {PLAIN}secret or {BLF-CRYPT}$2y$05$...
# No colons in password. Use LF line endings.

# Example (uid/gid 5000 = vmail in image):
# user1:{PLAIN}yourpassword:5000:5000::/home/mailhub-dovecot/maildir/user1::
# user2:{PLAIN}yourpassword:5000:5000::/home/mailhub-dovecot/maildir/user2::
